## How to Use

1. When a fix is applied, log it here with the matching date + stage from `error.log`.
2. Mark status as `WORKAROUND` if a proper fix is deferred.
3. Once verified in `7_Testing_Known`, update status to `VERIFIED`.

## Fix → Test Pipeline

```
error.log entry
    ↓
Root cause analysis (gap_analysis.md)
    ↓
Fix applied → fix.log entry (APPLIED)
    ↓
Validation in 7_Testing_Known
    ↓
fix.log entry updated (VERIFIED)
    ↓
Lesson captured in lessons_learned.md
```

